#. Description of the theme
#: style.css
msgid "An uncompromisingly accessible WordPress theme designed for everyone. Klaro features WCAG AAA color contrast, enabling users with disabilities to browse content and shop with WooCommerce independently. Includes adjustable text sizes, high contrast and monochrome modes, keyboard navigation, and screen reader optimization."
msgstr ""

